In addition, since $B$ is acute, $\sin B = \sqrt{1 - \frac{121}{169}} = \frac{4\sqrt{3}}{13}$, so
\[\tan B = \frac{\sin B}{\cos B} = \boxed{\frac{4 \sqrt{3}}{11}}.\]

